  "description": "Herbaceous annual from Solanaceae; domesticated in Mexico 7000+ years ago. Produces indeterminate or determinate inflorescence patterns, triggering continuous or terminal fruit set. Characterized by buzz-pollinated hermaphrodite flowers, carotenoid and lycopene accumulation in ripening fruit, and twining stoloniferous root systems.",
